
INFORMATION:
==========================================================
This e-learning platform is an simply platform. Its supports an easy
way of creating an e-learning offer by using a simple XML syntax structure.


REQUIREMENTS:
==========================================================
o PHP version 5.3 or higher
o Database support (e.g. MySQL or SQLite)
o cakePHP version 2.x
o Any webserver system supporting cakePHP, e.g. Apache


INSTALLATION:
==========================================================
All needed cakePHP changes are placed in the src-folder.
If you have any cakePHP source version you can copy the
content of the folder into a clean copy.

If you like to set-up an clean installation of cakePHP
and the e-learning platform, simply run the setup script
on any *nix system you like. NOTE: The script needs curl!

